This is a rough soundboard tape from AC/DCs Who made who - North America Tour 1986. No mic was turned towards the audience, 
so you will hardly notice any audience noise between the songs. It was one of the best sets ever including 
"She's got balls" which has not been played since 1977, also the last time to hear a live version of "Fly on the wall".
